---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <section class="text-center py-12">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Knowledge That Compounds</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 mb-8">
        AI without persistent memory is a brilliant colleague with amnesia. 
        Every conversation starts from zero.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100 mb-8">
        From first brain-master.md to 12-Brain network with 14 standards, 
        a book, and incorporated company. <strong>14 days.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/ktc" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">
          Learn the Method
        </a>
        <a href="/consulting" class="bg-gray-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-600">
          Work With Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 border-t border-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Problem</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100 mb-4">
        Every AI conversation starts from zero. Context disappears between sessions. 
        Knowledge gets lost. You repeat yourself constantly.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100">
        It's like having a brilliant colleague who forgets everything overnight.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 border-t border-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100 mb-4">
        Build systems where knowledge persists, compounds, and routes intelligently 
        across specialized AI "Brains."
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100">
        This is Knowledge That Compounds.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>